{
  "texts": [
    "A framework for remote patient monitoring using Ethereum smart contracts is presented in [44].",
    "WBAN's data is gathered and aggregated using a smart device like a laptop or smartphone.",
    "The smart gadget transmits the compiled data to a predetermined smart contract that is kept on Ethereum.",
    "The smart contract analyses the data and notifies smart devices and healthcare professionals of the outcome.",
    "The cloud stores the data, whereas the blockchain just records the event's occurrence."
  ]
}